reviewText: The movie is great, but Amazon's video quality and sound quality on this print is horrible I cannot believe they even charged for it. They need to get a better copy and replace everybody's copy with it.

I love Japanese sci fi movies from the 50's and 60's but this particular one the digital copy is SOOO BAD you can hardly see what is going on. The color has bled out, and the movie is cropped. AMAZON, please retire this move!
Excellent quality. Loved it, even if it is a b-movie scifi. It's class!
